{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484850/extras/Clean.gif?t=1738293329\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Struggling under crushing debt, you arrive in a mysterious town with one mission: survival. Your first job as a street cleaner helps keep the town tidy to attract travelers, but it barely scratches the surface of what you need to make ends meet.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484850/extras/Crime.gif?t=1738293329\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">To truly survive, you'll have to bend the rules\u2014or break them entirely. Steal, gamble, kidnap, or explore other underhanded ways to earn quick cash. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484850/extras/Ads.gif?t=1738293329\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Once you've scraped together your first fortune, it\u2019s time to expand. Build your empire by running a scam centre, posting scam advertisements, and tricking unsuspecting victims.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484850/extras/Mange.gif?t=1738293329\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You'll manage every aspect of your scam centre. Keep your workers productive\u2014or exploit them until there's nothing left. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The choices are yours, but in this town, only the cunning thrive. Will you rise to dominate, or will the weight of your choices drag you down?</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484850/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738293329","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_ite